In the observation (looking at the status) resource found at http://build.fhir.org/observation.html, what does registered mean? I haven't found any documentation on it. I know what preliminary, final, and amended means but registered doesn't click.

I found it, sorry.

http://build.fhir.org/valueset-observation-status.html "The existence of the observation is registered, but there is no result yet available."
